dc_title_s: Plat book of Clare County, Michigan
dc_description_s: Extent: 1 atlas (19 unnumbered pages) | Abstract: Atlas of township property maps showing names of rural landowners. | Notes: Cover missing.|Publication date estimated by the existence of highway 27 and no M-61 east of Harrison on folded map.|Scale determined from section lines.|Page 2 is a folded county map.|Includes advertisements for local businesses. | Scale approximately 1:51,000
